.modal-form.modal{z-index:9999}
.modal-form.modal&gt;.modal-dialog .modal-content{height:85%}
.modal-form.modal&gt;.modal-dialog .modal-sucess-msg .close-success-msg{position:absolute;right:15px;font-size:28px;top:7px;-webkit-transform:scale(1.25,1.0);-moz-transform:scale(1.25,1.0);-ms-transform:scale(1.25,1.0);-o-transform:scale(1.25,1.0);transform:scale(1.25,1.0);cursor:pointer}
.modal-form.modal&gt;.modal-dialog .modal-sucess-msg{background-color:#fff;padding:15px;margin:150px 0 0;display:none}
.modal-form.modal&gt;.modal-dialog .modal-sucess-msg&gt;p{margin-top:25px}
.modal-form.modal&gt;.modal-dialog .modal-header .logo{background-repeat:no-repeat;background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,);background-size:36px 36px;display:inline-block;float:left;height:36px;width:36px;margin:0 15px 0 0}
.modal-form.modal&gt;.modal-dialog .modal-body form{display:block;width:100% !important;margin:0 auto 25px}
